name: IBL Builder
tag_list: ibl, inbound-links, inlinks, backlinks, backlinking, linkjuice, one-way-linking, genuine-inbound-links
overview:
IBL Builder makes non-reciprocal linking, reciprocal. It is a complete inbound linkbuilding system, backed with link management tools to make managing continuous inbound link growth and management easy.

Born out of the frustration of trying to get genuine inbound links, IBL Builder has been built from the ground up to revolutionise the way people get inbound links. IBL Builder is not a reciprocal, triangle or automated linking tool.

Anyone who owns a website or blog can benefit from using IBL Builder to gain and manage relevant inound links, with targeted anchor text, to boost their search engine rankings.
